    <section name="SchemaCrawler - Maven Project Example">
      <subsection name="Description">
        <p>The SchemaCrawler Maven Project example demonstrates the use of
          the SchemaCrawler API
          in a Maven project.
        </p>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="How to Run">
        <ol>
          <li>
            Install
            <a href="http://maven.apache.org/">
              Maven,
            </a>
            and make sure that Maven is on your path
          </li>
          <li>
            Run
            <span class="code">mvn package</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            See the jar file produced in the
            <span class="code">target</span>
            directory
          </li>
        </ol>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="How to Experiment">
        <ol>
          <li>Try defining a new database connection, using your favorite
            database and driver.
          </li>
        </ol>
      </subsection>
    </section>
